title: Section

A //section// of a vector bundle $$\pi\colon E\to M$$ is a smooth map $$\sigma\colon M\to E$$ such that $$\pi\circ\sigma=\id_M,$$ meaning $$\sigma(p)\in E_p$$ for each $$p\in M.$$ The space of all (smooth) sections is denoted $$\Gamma(E).$$